PrecisAppointment of ROBERT GREENHILL, President of the Canadian International Development Agency (CIDA), as Alternate Governor of the International Bank of Reconstruction and Development (IBRD); and as Alternate Governor of the Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency (MIGA), to hold office during pleasure, in the place of Paul Thibault.
